8
00:00:30,250 --> 00:00:32,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">在和真宵聊过天的今宵</font>

9
00:00:32,140 --> 00:00:33,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就让我们回顾一下不久之前</font>

10
