13
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:46,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}虽说是文化祭  但我们已经是三年级了</font>

14
00:00:46,680 --> 00:00:48,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}也没什么好做的事情了</font>

15
00:00:47,490 --> 00:00:52,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那天放学后  我和失去了黄金周记忆的羽川翼一起</font>

16
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:55,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">商谈关于下周要举办的文化节的事情</font>

17
00:00:56,730 --> 00:01:00,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个  我们班上有个叫战场原的吧</font>

18
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:05,590
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">战场原同学说话不多  而且好像一个朋友也没有</font>

19
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:08,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">果然是因为生病的缘故吗</font>

20
00:01:08,890 --> 00:01:13,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">初中的时候她还是个精力充沛活泼开朗的女孩子来着</font>

21
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还真是少见啊</font>

22
00:01:16,250 --> 00:01:19,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">阿良良木君竟然会对别人感兴趣</font>

23
00:01:23,180 --> 00:01:26,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你和羽川同学谈了些什么</font>

24
00:01:30,460 --> 00:01:31,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不要动</font>

25
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:34,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好奇心就像蟑螂一样啊</font>

26
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:38,440
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就喜欢扑到人们不想被触及的秘密上来</font>

27
00:01:38,930 --> 00:01:40,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">真是烦得让人受不了</font>

28
00:01:41,140 --> 00:01:41,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">喂</font>

29
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么  右边的脸很寂寞吗</font>

30
00:01:45,240 --> 00:01:47,410
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那样的话你跟我说不就行了</font>

31
00:01:47,740 --> 00:01:49,080
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你发现了吧</font>

32
00:01:49,810 --> 00:01:50,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">是的</font>

33
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:54,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我没有…重量</font>

34
00:01:55,180 --> 00:01:57,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我遇到了一只螃蟹</font>

35
00:01:57,900 --> 00:01:59,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">体重被一点不剩地夺走了</font>

36
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:05,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么  为了让你保守我的秘密</font>

37
00:02:05,660 --> 00:02:07,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我应该做些什么呢</font>

38
00:02:07,740 --> 00:02:10,920
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我应该为了我自己做些什么呢</font>

39
00:02:15,420 --> 00:02:16,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那么  阿良良木君</font>

40
00:02:17,020 --> 00:02:19,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">从明天起要好好无视我哦</font>

41
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:20,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">请多关照</font>

42
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:24,730
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">现在回想起来依然会不禁打起寒颤</font>

43
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">简直是像恶魔一样的女人</font>

44
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:33,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是  为了死守自己的秘密便这般将他人拒之门外的战场原</font>

45
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:39,320
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">显然已经无助得走投无路  于是我想助她一臂之力</font>

46
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:40,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">战场原</font>

47
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:46,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">伤口…消失了</font>

48
00:02:46,970 --> 00:02:49,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你…这是怎么回事</font>

49
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">重蟹</font>

50
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:54,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">重蟹？</font>

51
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:58,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  是九州那边山里的民间传说</font>

52
00:02:58,940 --> 00:03:02,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">根据地域不同有重蟹  重物蟹  重石蟹等叫法</font>

53
00:03:03,290 --> 00:03:05,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">另外还有重石神这种叫法</font>

54
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:07,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也就是因为谐音而把蟹和神关联起来了</font>

55
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:09,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不要误会了哦  小姐</font>

56
00:03:09,450 --> 00:03:11,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你并不是因为做错了什么而变成这样的</font>

57
00:03:11,820 --> 00:03:13,390
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只是视点稍微改变了一下而已</font>

58
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你到底想说什么</font>

59
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:18,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我是说我看不惯你摆出一副被害者的样子  小姐</font>

60
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:28,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗬  真是了不起啊  我还以为只是个任性的大小姐呢</font>

61
00:03:29,090 --> 00:03:31,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为什么  你会这么想</font>

62
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:35,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">因为会遇到重蟹的人基本上都是这样的</font>

63
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:39,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不是想见就能见得到的  那可是一般人接触不到的神</font>

64
00:03:40,780 --> 00:03:42,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">它只是存在于那里</font>

65
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:45,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果不是小姐你有什么期望的话它是不会出现的</font>

66
00:03:45,660 --> 00:03:47,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">总之没问题  我明白了</font>

67
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:51,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果你想取回体重的话  我可以帮你</font>

68
00:03:51,610 --> 00:03:53,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你愿意救我吗</font>

69
00:03:55,570 --> 00:03:56,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我不会救你的</font>

70
00:03:57,010 --> 00:03:58,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但我可以借你些力量</font>

71
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这样吧  你先回一趟家</font>

72
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:07,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后用冷水把身体洗干净  换身干净的衣服</font>

73
00:04:13,970 --> 00:04:17,720
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">羽川说战场原家过去曾是豪宅</font>

74
00:04:18,130 --> 00:04:21,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我妈妈沉迷于可疑的宗教</font>

75
00:04:21,570 --> 00:04:26,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不仅将家产全都捐了出去  还背上了巨额的债务</font>

76
00:04:28,410 --> 00:04:31,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">结果在去年年末  我父母终于协议离婚</font>

77
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:36,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我由父亲抚养  在这里和他一起生活</font>

78
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:43,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">洗净身体后我们再次来到忍野所在的私塾废墟</font>

79
00:04:54,260 --> 00:04:58,700
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是忍野  那个螃蟹还是什么东西是这么简单就能退治的吗？</font>

80
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你想问题的方式还真粗鲁啊  阿良良木君</font>

81
00:05:03,250 --> 00:05:06,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我不是说了吗  对方是神</font>

82
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:11,550
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所以说不是退治它  现在开始我们要向神祈求</font>

83
00:05:11,930 --> 00:05:13,060
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">要用谦恭的态度</font>

84
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:16,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只要求它  它就会把那些还回来吗</font>

85
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:17,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">战场原的…</font>

86
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:20,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">重量  体重</font>

87
00:05:21,010 --> 00:05:22,010
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">也许吧</font>

88
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:28,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">然后就在废弃大楼的三楼  忍野已经布置过的房间里</font>

89
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">进行了仪式</font>

90
00:05:32,100 --> 00:05:33,890
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好的  那么来回答我的问题</font>

91
00:05:34,100 --> 00:05:36,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">小姐  你的名字是？</font>

92
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">所就读的学校是？</font>

93
00:05:37,240 --> 00:05:38,200
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">生日是？</font>

94
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:41,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">迄今为止的人生中  最痛苦的回忆是？</font>

95
00:05:44,660 --> 00:05:48,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">妈妈她沉迷于邪恶的宗教</font>

96
00:05:48,170 --> 00:05:50,170
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（回答问题）</font>

97
00:05:49,130 --> 00:05:50,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">只有这些吗？</font>

98
00:05:51,820 --> 00:05:59,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">妈妈…带着那个宗教团体的干部来到家里</font>

99
00:06:00,050 --> 00:06:01,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">来了之后  发生了什么</font>

100
00:06:02,940 --> 00:06:05,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说是一种仪式  对我…</font>

101
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,260
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对我…</font>

102
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,310
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（要求进行性行为）</font>

103
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:10,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">施暴</font>

104
00:06:14,740 --> 00:06:17,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">想要侵犯我</font>

105
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:21,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然说是「想」要侵犯  那就是未遂是吧</font>

106
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:25,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我用身边的钉鞋打了他</font>

107
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:31,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是  妈妈…却没有来救我</font>

108
00:06:31,850 --> 00:06:35,290
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不要逃避  睁开眼睛看看吧</font>

109
00:06:39,050 --> 00:06:39,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}<font size="27">蟹
【a crab】
