110
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:43,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和那个时候一样的</font>

111
00:06:43,570 --> 00:06:46,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">和那个时候一样的大螃蟹</font>

112
00:06:47,410 --> 00:06:49,160
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我看见了…一只螃蟹</font>

113
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">战…战场原！</font>

114
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:25,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说到底这种事主要是心灵沟通的问题</font>

115
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:29,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">如果祈求不管用  语言上无法沟通的话</font>

116
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:31,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那就只能靠战争了</font>

117
00:07:32,930 --> 00:07:33,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">等等…</font>

118
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:36,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">请等一下  忍野先生</font>

119
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:39,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我…能做到</font>

120
00:07:39,810 --> 00:07:41,760
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我自己能和它沟通</font>

121
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:45,740
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那就请吧  你来试试看</font>

122
00:07:49,650 --> 00:07:50,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对不起</font>

123
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:54,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">还有  谢谢您了</font>

124
00:07:55,730 --> 00:07:57,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是  已经足够了</font>

125
00:07:57,780 --> 00:08:02,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那都是我的心情  是我的回忆  是我的记忆</font>

126
00:08:02,820 --> 00:08:04,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一切都由我自己来承担</font>

127
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:07,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那是我不可失去的东西</font>

128
00:08:07,520 --> 00:08:11,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">请将妈妈…还给我吧</font>

129
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:15,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（以下 回想）</font>

130
00:08:16,170 --> 00:08:19,810
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">战场原的母亲迷上邪教</font>

131
00:08:20,130 --> 00:08:23,150
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">似乎是在战场原小学五年级的时候</font>

132
00:08:23,150 --> 00:08:24,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（野兽一般的眼神）</font>

133
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,080
